title: Ep 97: The Aftermath
description: What. The. Fuck. Yup, it happened. Trump is president. Now what? Let's process this then answer some emails. A gay man just came out to his family and has regrets. Also, do you have to be a sociopath to succeed in life? Let's get deep on ALLLLLL of this, bros.
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
